\change_unchanged
the results expecially when 
\change_deleted 1286759212 1694193581
 
\change_unchanged
rebuilding demand is taken into account.
 Simulations show high sensitivity to parameter 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

 and rebuilding duration in this case.
 Rebuilding durations that are too short especially lead to large indirect
