\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
These elements show that results are heavily dependent on assumptions about
 rebuilding and the rigidity of constraints on the actors.
 This aligns with existing studies that have shown both positive and negative
 indirect impacts following a shock.
 We observe that the ARIO model can both lead to negative and positive impacts
 (the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

creative destruction
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 hypothesis).
