\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "app1.3.2"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
There are multiple parameters, which are difficult to calibrate, notably
 because of a lack of empirical data (inventory size, characteristic times,
